# HeroesProfile official API token.
# Get it from the HeroesProfile Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Heroesprofile
# When set, /api/meta serves real Storm League win/pick/ban rates from
# api.heroesprofile.com. When empty, it falls back to the Icy-Veins tier list.
#
# Local dev: copy this file to `.env` and fill in the token (Vite loads it).
# Netlify:   set HEROESPROFILE_API_TOKEN in Site settings → Environment variables.
HEROESPROFILE_API_TOKEN=
